button.description:
## Description développeur
Composant généré par le pipeline IA avec fidélité pixel-perfect Figma. À compléter par le développeur.

## Token Mapping (Figma → CSS)
radius: {radius.md} → var(--component-button-radius, var(--semantic-radius-md))
borderWidth: {borderWidth.default} → var(--semantic-border-width-default)
fontWeight: {font.weight.semibold} → var(--semantic-font-weight-semibold)
fontFamily: {font.family.default} → var(--semantic-font-family-default)
focus.ringColor: {color.primary.500} → var(--semantic-color-primary-500)
sm.paddingX: {spacing.sm} → var(--semantic-spacing-sm)
sm.paddingY: {spacing.xs} → var(--semantic-spacing-xs)
sm.fontSize: {font.size.sm} → var(--semantic-font-size-sm)
sm.gap: {spacing.xs} → var(--semantic-spacing-xs)
md.paddingX: {spacing.md} → var(--semantic-spacing-md)
md.paddingY: {spacing.sm} → var(--semantic-spacing-sm)
md.fontSize: {font.size.sm} → var(--semantic-font-size-sm)
md.gap: {spacing.sm} → var(--semantic-spacing-sm)
lg.paddingX: {spacing.lg} → var(--semantic-spacing-lg)
lg.paddingY: {spacing.sm} → var(--semantic-spacing-sm)
lg.fontSize: {font.size.md} → var(--semantic-font-size-md)
lg.gap: {spacing.sm} → var(--semantic-spacing-sm)
primary.bg: #d90a79 → var(--component-button-primary-bg)
primary.border: #d90a79 → var(--component-button-primary-border)
hover.bg: #1D4ED8 → var(--component-button-primary-hover-bg)
secondary.bg: #FFFFFF → var(--component-button-secondary-bg)
secondary.border: #D1D5DB → var(--component-button-secondary-border)
secondary.color: #374151 → var(--component-button-secondary-color)
ghost.bg: transparent → var(--component-button-ghost-bg)
ghost.color: #374151 → var(--component-button-ghost-color)
danger.bg: #DC2626 → var(--component-button-danger-bg)

## Do & Don't
✅ **Do**
- Utiliser les CSS custom properties (var(--component-*))
- Respecter les états interactifs (hover, active, focus, disabled)
- Vérifier la fidélité visuelle avec la maquette Figma

❌ **Don't**
- Ne pas utiliser de valeurs brutes (px, #hex) — utiliser les tokens
- Ne pas supprimer les états d'accessibilité (:focus-visible)
- Ne pas modifier les dimensions sans vérifier la spec Figma

## 💻 Code interactif (Live Editor)

```jsx
const __css = `.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: var(--semantic-font-family-default, Inter);
  font-weight: var(--semantic-font-weight-semibold, 600);
  border-radius: var(--component-button-radius, var(--semantic-radius-md, 8px));
  border: var(--semantic-border-width-default, 1px) solid transparent;
  transition: all 150ms ease-in-out;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-decoration: none;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.btn:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid var(--semantic-color-primary-500, #d90a79);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
.btn:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }

/* Sizes */
.btn--sm {
  padding: var(--semantic-spacing-xs, 4px) var(--semantic-spacing-sm, 8px);
  font-size: var(--semantic-font-size-sm, 14px);
  line-height: 20px;
  gap: var(--semantic-spacing-xs, 4px);
  min-height: 32px;
}
.btn--md {
  padding: var(--semantic-spacing-sm, 8px) var(--semantic-spacing-md, 16px);
  font-size: var(--semantic-font-size-sm, 14px);
  line-height: 20px;
  gap: var(--semantic-spacing-sm, 8px);
  min-height: 40px;
}
.btn--lg {
  padding: var(--semantic-spacing-sm, 8px) var(--semantic-spacing-lg, 24px);
  font-size: var(--semantic-font-size-md, 16px);
  line-height: 24px;
  gap: var(--semantic-spacing-sm, 8px);
  min-height: 48px;
}

/* Variants */
.btn--primary {
  background: var(--component-button-primary-bg, #d90a79);
  border-color: var(--component-button-primary-border, #d90a79);
  color: #fff;
}
.btn--primary:hover:not(:disabled) { background: var(--component-button-primary-hover-bg, #1D4ED8); border-color: var(--component-button-primary-hover-bg, #1D4ED8); }

.btn--secondary {
  background: var(--component-button-secondary-bg, #FFFFFF);
  border-color: var(--component-button-secondary-border, #D1D5DB);
  color: var(--component-button-secondary-color, #374151);
}

.btn--ghost {
  background: transparent;
  border-color: transparent;
  color: var(--component-button-ghost-color, #374151);
}

.btn--danger {
  background: var(--component-button-danger-bg, #DC2626);
  border-color: var(--component-button-danger-bg, #DC2626);
  color: #fff;
}`;

const Button = ({
  variant = "primary",
  size = "md",
  disabled = false,
  children,
  onClick,
  type = "button",
  ...props
}) => (
  <button
    type={type}
    className={`btn btn--${variant} btn--${size}`}
    disabled={disabled}
    onClick={onClick}
    {...props}
  >
    {children}
  </button>
);

// Demo
const ButtonDemo = () => (
  <div style={{ display: "flex", flexWrap: "wrap", gap: 8, padding: 16 }}>
    <Button size="sm">Small</Button>
    <Button size="md">Medium</Button>
    <Button size="lg">Large</Button>
    <Button variant="secondary">Secondary</Button>
    <Button variant="ghost">Ghost</Button>
    <Button variant="danger">Danger</Button>
    <Button disabled>Disabled</Button>
  </div>
);

render(<><style>{__css}</style><Button /></>);
```

## ⚠️ Tokens manquants (à créer dans Figma)
--component-button-primary-bg | background | #d90a79
--component-button-primary-border | border-color | #d90a79
--component-button-primary-hover-bg | background:hover | #1D4ED8
--component-button-secondary-bg | background | #FFFFFF
--component-button-secondary-border | border-color | #D1D5DB
--component-button-secondary-color | color | #374151
--component-button-ghost-color | color | #374151
--component-button-danger-bg | background | #DC2626
--semantic-color-primary-500 | focus ring color | #d90a79

